data.description: TURN KEY LAKE HOUSE! Check out this amazing home located at Tobacco Gardens on Lake Sakakawea!  In this 2,280 SQFT home you will find 2 spacious family/living rooms, a large kitchen and dining room with tons of storage, a relaxing primary suite, 2 additional bedrooms, 1 additional bathroom, an office, a laundry room and a storage room.  Outside you will find a heated 1,512 SQFT, 3 stall detached garage/shop with an exercise room partitioned off.  The front yard offers a large deck, raised garden beds, pull through driveway, and a large yard.  In the back yard you will find another large deck, a firepit, 2 garden/storage sheds-1 with electricity, and lots of room to play!  All around the property you will find mature trees and landscaping.
